acceptance_criteria: Latest pm CLI/SDK dependency is used; pm-changelog release scripts are present where applicable; package tests and release checks pass or blockers are recorded; no private data is introduced; results are captured in pm history.
notes[3]{created_at,author,text}:
  "2026-06-12T12:12:07.264Z",codex,"Private pm-web release-readiness pass: removed GitHub CI/release workflows to avoid GitHub runners and npm publish for the private website, aligned pm CLI/pm-changelog dependencies, regenerated CHANGELOG.md, and release checks passed through typecheck/build/test/changelog. npm audit --omit=dev failed repeatedly on 2026-06-12 with registry ETIMEDOUT against npm advisory bulk endpoint; no vulnerability report was returned. Full public-safe history scan remains incomplete; current tracked-file grep found expected env variable names only, not literal credentials."
  "2026-06-12T14:01:41.428Z",codex,"Verified release readiness after moving @unbrained/pm-cli to runtime dependencies: npm release:check completed for the fleet on 2026-06-12; npm audit retries for pm-beads and pm-jira returned 0 vulnerabilities after transient advisory endpoint failures."
  "2026-06-12T14:04:18.239Z",codex,"History secret-pattern scan found env-var name references such as OLLAMA_API_KEY assignments to empty strings in historical source/dist, not literal tokens. pm-web remains private and was not approved for public history."
body: "Align to latest published @unbrained/pm-cli, align pm-changelog where applicable, verify changelog/release commands, run tests with real package data, and record upstream pm CLI/SDK UX issues separately in unbraind/pm-cli."
